data.description: "HIDDEN FALLS" is Back on the Market Buyer walked Away at no fault of Seller and home is priced below appraised value. Owner says, bring all "reasonable offers!" The awesome home sits on  2.4 acres of a private & secluded wildlife preservation that will take you away from hustle and bustle of everyday life.This is your chance to buy your own slice of paradise in the city and get it at a price and interest rate that is a deal! From the rollout windows in each room you can enjoy the sights and sounds of the waterfall, pond, and creek that attract a heron for regular visits, and  meadows that attract the deer; Hydrangeas & Rhododendrons attract Hummingbirds, Cardinals, and Blue Jays. Spend your evenings listening to the  Whippoorwills and Owls, touring the grounds and identifying the numerous fruit trees, shrubbery, and flowers while inhaling the sweet aroma of Camelia bushes. You can even take time to explore the bamboo grove or saunter along the walking trail that follows the Creek. The original owner of this unique property was a horticulturist, and her expertise is displayed in every inch of this property; She designed this custom built  home to blend harmoniously with its surroundings and the landscape while offering stunning views of the pond, waterfall and creek from every main room of the house. The home offers not only a sense of family but also privacy as all 6 bedrooms feature a private bath area. Three of the bedrooms even offer private access to either patio or observation decks, which reach across the entire back back of the home. The 125+ feet of decks and patios provide 3 different levels to relax and absorb the tranquility of the sights, the sounds, and the aromatic fragrances of nature; from the smells of flowers, the rush of water as it pours over the falls, the babbling creek, the beautiful surroundings and the gentle breeze against your skin, the property simply overwhelms the senses and provides a level of peace and serenity that makes you feel miles away from everything. Besides being an Oasis of Tranquility in the Chaos of the City, the home provides a perfect setting for entertaining. Outside offers opportunities, such as cookouts and playing family games in the spacious yard; while the bright, airy, and cheery interior brings the outdoors inside as natural light streams through the wall to wall windows. The space feels cavernous thanks to the cathedral ceiling and open floor plan in the Great Room, which even has a fireplace for cozying up on cool winter evenings. The spacious kitchen featuring wrap around cabinetry, under counter lighting in a layout that makes baking and cooking for friends and family a breeze with over 30' of countertops, a built-in pantry swing for easy access to all items, and even 2 corner cabinets that each feature a lazy-Susan rack.  Even chores, such as Laundry, are easier to do in this home, which features a huge Laundry room that currently touts 2 washers and 2 dryers as well as storage shelving, and even a window to enjoy the natural beauty of the exterior. The home also features multiple Water Heaters. A Tankless water heater that was installed last year services the main house and master wing while a gas fired tanked water heater services the two bathrooms on the far side of the home. The Spacious-Oversized Downstairs Den is bright and open with more wall to wall windows and gorgeous ground level waterfall views. Perhaps even better,  more views of the Waterfall can be enjoyed in the Privacy of the Master bedroom, which features, a sitting area, walk in closet, more windows & views, and a private patio. The walkway to the home is an hourglass with the dark stones the white stones are the sand falling in the hourglass.  So many details were given to this home and too numerous to mention.  This private paradise park acreage is only minutes to restaurants, shopping, and schools. Do Not Miss this one of a kind property you will never find anywhere else in Spartanburg.
